    "stdyInfo": {
      "abstract": [
        {
          "contentType": "purpose",
          "lang": "fr",
          "value": "Etudier les liens entre la dépression, l'anxiété (y compris la phobie sociale), les symptômes obsessionnels du comportement et de l'alimentation et l'état nutritionnel à l'admission (Indice de Masse Corporelle IMC et ampleur de la perte de poids) et la durée de la maladie. Ainsi que l'évolution à long terme de l'IMC."
        },
        {
          "contentType": "purpose",
          "lang": "en",
          "value": "To study the relationship between depression, anxiety (including social phobia), obsessive behaviour and eating symptoms and nutritional status on admission (Body Mass Index (BMI) and extent of weight loss), as well as the duration of the illness. Long-term BMI progress is also included."
        }
      ],
